data.description: Beautiful MOVING READY BLOCK Home has 3 Bedrooms & 1 Bathroom with 1 Car Garage in Shamrock Heights! The refreshed kitchen includes appliances, granite countertops and fixtures. The bathroom has been completely remodeled. Laminate Floors through out the home NOT Carpet. Home offers ample space with separate living rooms and Dining room. Enjoy the lush landscaped backyard. Convenient location close to amenities such as shopping, dining, and grocery stores. Enjoy Florida living on the nearby beaches and parks! Home is selling AS IS with the right of inspection. Roof 2011, septic tank system is 2020.  Flood Insurance is transferable and Seller has an Elevation Certificate and Survey. Less money the next buyer will have to spend. ***SELLER WON'T ENTERTAIN LOW BALL OFFERS***
